      <file>.claude/constraints/bff-extensions.md</file>
    </files>
  </knowledge>

  <steps>
    <step order="1">Load architecture §6.3 (recall flow diagram), §8.1 (schema), §8.3 (trust framing), §5.2.1 (NOT spaarke-insights-index), §9.2 (graceful errors).</step>
    <step order="2">Read `RagService.cs` to confirm the SearchAsync signature + filter syntax for `spaarke-session-files` index.</step>
    <step order="3">Author `Services/Ai/Handlers/RecallSessionFileHandler.cs` implementing `IToolHandler`. Parameters: `fileId` (required), `purpose` (required enum), `query` (required), `scope` (required enum, default `relevant_sections`), `maxTokens` (optional), `requireCitations` (optional, DEFAULT true).</step>
    <step order="4">Implement mode dispatch per §6.3:
      (a) `summary` → read `ChatSession.UploadedFiles[fileId].PrecomputedSummary` (hot path);
      (b) `relevant_sections` / `tables` / `citations` → `RagService.SearchAsync(index: "spaarke-session-files", filter: $"session_file_id eq '{fileId}'", query, topK: 3)` — bias by `purpose` per FR-31;
      (c) `full_text` → if total ≤8K tokens, concat chunks; else return summary + first 2K chars + `truncation_reason: "exceeded_8K"`.
    </step>
    <step order="5">After successful recall (any mode except not_found), mark `IRecentlyDiscussedTracker.Mark(sessionId, fileId)` — task 091 ensures this dependency is registered.</step>
    <step order="6">Emit `context.tool_call_completed` event for T6 audit per architecture §6.3 — tier-1 safe (no content).</step>
    <step order="7">Add Dataverse seed-row JSON `infra/dataverse/sprk_analysistool-recall-session-file-row.json` with full parameter schema in `sprk_parameterschema`.</step>
    <step order="8">Author unit tests covering: 6 purposes × 5 scopes (matrix), not_found path, exceeded_8K truncation path, recentlyDiscussed mark side-effect, ADR-015 telemetry safety, `requireCitations: true` default verified via metadata.</step>
    <step order="9">Run `dotnet build` + `dotnet test`. Must pass.</step>
    <step order="10">Run grep across the new handler file: `grep -i "spaarke-insights-index"` must return ZERO matches (architecture §5.2.1 enforcement).</step>
    <step order="11">Measure BFF publish-size delta; write `notes/handoffs/085-bff-publish-delta.md`.</step>
    <step order="12">Run code-review + adr-check (Step 9.5).</step>
    <step order="13">Update TASK-INDEX.md: 085 → ✅.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="Read">RagService.cs, ChatSession model, exemplar handler</tool>
    <tool name="Write">Handler + tests + seed-row JSON</tool>
    <tool name="Grep">Verify zero references to spaarke-insights-index</tool>
    <tool name="Bash">dotnet build / test / publish</tool>
  </tools>

  <outputs>
    <output type="code">src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/Handlers/RecallSessionFileHandler.cs</output>
